text: Central Street can refer to: * Central Street (Evanston, IL), a major east- west road and shopping district in Evanston, Illinois * Central (CTA Purple Line), a station in Evanston, Illinois on the Chicago Transit Authority's 'L' system * Evanston Central Street (Metra), a commuter rail stop in Evanston, Illinois * Central Street District, a historic district along Central Street in Andover, Massachusetts * Central Street Historic District (Narragansett, Rhode Island) * Central Street Historic District (Millville, Massachusetts) * Central Street (Harbin, China), a historical pedestrian street in Harbin, China
title: Central Street
